  "title": "IT Engineer (Manufacturing, ITOT, East Region)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong> </p><ul><li>Provision and onboard OT network tools.</li><li>Coordinate with network teams for switch port, trunking, and tagging setup.</li><li>Ensure secure and compliant tool connectivity with cross-functional teams.</li><li>Work with cybersecurity team on risk validation and mitigation.</li><li> Apply project management skills to support activities.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements: </strong></p><ul><li>Minimum 3 years’ experience in IT infrastructure, networking, or cybersecurity.</li><li>Hands-on experience with VLANs, IP setup, and firewall rules (Check Point or similar).</li><li>Experience in security assessments and risk evaluations.</li><li>Exposure to IT/OT integration or industrial environments preferred.</li></ul><p><strong>______________________________________________________</strong></p><p><strong>HOW TO APPLY :</strong></p><p><strong>Interested candidates, please submit your resume by clicking on “Quick Apply” or contact win@hkmsvs.com for more details.</strong></p><p><strong>Please provide following information in the resume for immediate processing</strong></p><p><strong>1) Reasons for leaving current and/or last employment</strong></p><p><strong>2) Last drawn and/or current salary</strong></p><p><strong>3) Expected salary</strong></p><p><strong>4) Date of availability and/or Notice Period</strong></p><p><strong>All applications will be treated in strictest confidence and only shortlisted candidates will be notified</strong></p><p><strong>Wee Wai Dan</strong></p><p><strong>EA License No : 03C5391</strong></p><p><strong>EA Reg No : R22109628</strong></p>",
